    {
      "note": "Summary of Original Version",
      "abstract": "Repeal, reenact as a new section of KRS Chapter 365, and amend KRS 369.135 to define \"credit card\" and \"debit card\"; expand section, relating to the use of a digital asset as a method of payment, to apply to credit cards and debit cards."
